The tracking number assigned is 9205590153708404865982. You can use your tracking number at www.USPS.com in the Quick Tools Tracking section. If you did not receive the card, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request that we resend the card to you. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Correspondence Was Received And USCIS Is Reviewing It
body: On March 29, 2021, we received your correspondence for Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190072997. We are reviewing your correspondence, and will send you a notice if we need something from you. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Card Was Mailed To Me
body: On April 5, 2021, we mailed your new card for your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190072998, to the address you gave us. If you do not receive your card by April 20, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request that we send your new card to you. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Case Was Received
body: On February 18, 2021, we received your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190072999, and sent you the receipt notice that describes how we will process your case. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
